sellerAgent.name: Sean Healey and The Healey Home Selling Team Denver, CO Irvine, CA

data.description: Beautiful move in ready home! Entry level open, light, bright and inviting. Kitchen features new Dishwasher, Stove, Microwave Oven, counter tops and tile back splash! Main Level Laundry. Newer Paint throughout. Window Blinds included. Located across and down from Park. Sump Pump. Ceiling fan in main living area. Bathrooms have new bath tub with insert, tile and engineered flooring. Detached garage has a work bench and Alley access. Shed is attached to home and neighbors shed (builder installed)Yard features a great garden area, and stone pavers, wonderful for patio entertaining. Birdbath in yard, Sprinkling system, small Grassed area easy to maintain.  Pool Community with, Club house, Gym, Park, and Dog park.  Foundations Academy within walking distance! 30 Min Commute to Denver, and 20 Min Commute to DIA.
